data.description: Welcome home to your own piece of the historic West 7th Street neighborhood. This charming 3br bungalow is tucked away on a quiet dead end street just a short distance to scenic riverfront views. Natural lighting throughout emphasizes the woodwork and gorgeous original maple floors. Comes recently updated with newer appliances and a beautiful main floor bathroom, along with a stunning front porch and spacious 2 car garage. Countless dining and entertainment options available, just minutes away from downtown Saint Paul!
